id=audio_bridge
name=Audio Bridge
version=v3.1-samsung-vn
versionCode=310
author=AudioBridge
description=Remote audio + telephony control. Targets Samsung S20 / Note20 (Exynos 9830, KR variants) on KernelSU/Magisk. Captures app-call audio via Zygisk and cellular-call audio via VOICE_CALL AudioSource (requires priv-app install for CAPTURE_AUDIO_OUTPUT).
